'''海洋環保計劃'''（{{lang-en|Project AWARE}}），屬於由義工自願[[水肺潛水|水肺潛水]]人員，註冊成為[[非營利組織|非營利組織]]，它們兩項主要重點議題是「瀕臨絕種的鯊魚」(Sharks in Peril)，以及「清除海洋垃圾」(Marine Debris)的問題，與此同時，已有180個國家運作的<ref>[http://www.projectaware.org/about-movement 有關海洋環保計劃（英文版）] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160209125925/http://www.projectaware.org/about-movement |date=2016-02-09 }}</ref>。

==背景==
該基金會在1989年，由{{link-en|專業潛水指導委員會|Professional Association of Diving Instructors|}}發起設立<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.projectaware.org/our-story |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-04-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140419015401/http://www.projectaware.org/our-story |archivedate=2014-04-19 }}</ref><ref name=Cater2001>{{cite book |author=Cater, C; Cater, E. |page=271 |title=Marine environments In: Weaver, DB. The Encyclopedia of Ecotourism |year=2001 |isbn=0851993680 |url=http://books.google.com/books?hl=en&lr=&id=HhfHmSojJ8QC&oi=fnd&pg=PA265&dq=Aquatic+World+Awareness+Responsibility,+and+Education+1987&ots=AkZSlLieUS&sig=Pq_LpQbAPhUrHJ9Mj1_yzczWgwY#v=onepage&q&f=false |accessdate=2014-03-18 |archive-date=2014-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140629092649/http://books.google.com/books?hl=en&lr=&id=HhfHmSojJ8QC&oi=fnd&pg=PA265&dq=Aquatic+World+Awareness+Responsibility,+and+Education+1987&ots=AkZSlLieUS&sig=Pq_LpQbAPhUrHJ9Mj1_yzczWgwY#v=onepage&q&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>直至2008年，該會辦事處日本、瑞士、澳大利亞、英國和美國等地區，已成為最大地理營運環保組織<ref name=Townsend2008>{{cite book |author=Townsend, Claudia |title=Dive tourism, sustainable tourism and social responsibility: A growing agenda. In: Brian Garrod, Stefan Gössling (eds.) New Frontiers in Marine Tourism: Diving Experiences, Sustainability, Management |year=2008 |page=140 |isbn=9780080453576 |url=http://books.google.com/books?hl=en&lr=&id=JmbR1pEUFVcC&oi=fnd&pg=PA139&dq=Aquatic+World+Awareness+Responsibility,+and+Education+1987&ots=4k2Hu5Yl-u&sig=5o7AtjKLAPEIX_y52Dfrr2cmKHM#v=onepage&q&f=false |accessdate=2014-03-18 |archive-date=2014-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140629092602/http://books.google.com/books?hl=en&lr=&id=JmbR1pEUFVcC&oi=fnd&pg=PA139&dq=Aquatic+World+Awareness+Responsibility,+and+Education+1987&ots=4k2Hu5Yl-u&sig=5o7AtjKLAPEIX_y52Dfrr2cmKHM#v=onepage&q&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==活動==
該會還在年報披露了有關義工工作處理相關事件，包括參與打擊海洋垃圾潛水計畫(Diving Against Debris)、重植珊瑚救海洋、捐錢等<ref name="projectaware.org">{{cite web |url=http://www.projectaware.org/resource/year-review-2014 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-01-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150128114444/http://www.projectaware.org/resource/year-review-2014 |archivedate=2015-01-28 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.projectaware.org/project/dive-against-debris |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-12-02 |archive-date=2015-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222101349/http://www.projectaware.org/project/dive-against-debris |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.baynews9.com/content/news/baynews9/news/article.html/content/news/articles/bn9/2014/6/21/holmes_beach_clean.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-12-02 |archive-date=2015-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222135844/http://www.baynews9.com/content/news/baynews9/news/article.html/content/news/articles/bn9/2014/6/21/holmes_beach_clean.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>http://www.sportdiver.com/article/padi-news/project-aware-250-locations-and-counting-to-monitor-coral-reefs</ref><ref name=ReefCheck20008>{{cite web |author=staff |title=Reef Check Partners With Project AWARE Foundation |date=25 January 2008 |publisher={{link-en|珊瑚普查|Reef Check|}} |url=http://reefcheck.org/news/news_detail.php?id=312 |accessdate=2014-03-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140309024114/http://reefcheck.org/news/news_detail.php?id=312 |archivedate=2014年3月9日 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.guangming.com.my/node/154976?tid=48 生態保育（上篇）‧重植珊瑚救海洋] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guangming.com.my/node/154976?tid=48 |date=20160305020155 }}2012年12月29日 [[光明日報|光明日報]]</ref>。

